Insider Activity


Individual




Frank Slootman



Mr. Frank Slootman is Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer at ServiceNow, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Pure Storage, Inc. and Medallia, Inc. Mr. Slootman was previously employed as an Independent Director by Imperva, Inc., Venture Partner by Greylock Management Corp., President-Backup Recovery Systems Division by EMC Corp., President & Chief Executive Officer by Data Domain, Inc., Senior Vice President-Products by Borland Software Corp., a Principal by Compuware Corp., a Principal by Burroughs Corp., and General Manager by Ecosystems SRL. He received his undergraduate degree from Erasmus University Rotterdam and a graduate degree from Erasmus University Rotterdam.



